{
  "stem": "6762.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't want to go to underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not me, I had enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have enough of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I guess he went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I stayed there and somehow got connection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to Munich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I worked for the office JDC, for the Joint.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the American, um, organization to help Jews after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was their-- I was like a patrolman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What shall I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it took over a building from the Germans, big, big building was [? a. ?] And over there was living this, the, the American MP lived there, and the-- and the worker from the military, the PO, or the post office, from the military.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, those guys [INAUDIBLE] who worked for the-- for JDD-- for the DC-- for the Joint.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a good job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Compared to what I had before, I had a good job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have a nice apartment, you know, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I make a little bit black marketeering there with the, with the, with the soldiers and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had it all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in 1948, on the end-- I wanted to go before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It didn't-- didn't work it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wanted to go before to Israel, to Palestine through Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't work it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So end of '48, just about beginning of '49, actually it was in February, I went to-- to, uh-- Israel?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said [INAUDIBLE] Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With the [NON-ENGLISH], with the ship there, it was awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we slept way, three floors down, all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And still wasn't-- so was still the war a little bit going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even they finished the war, you were fighting with the Arabs still, anyways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I came there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
